INSERT INTO mw_text VALUES (1601,'This is a short HowTo remotly control a Zaurus (or something else!) through VNC.\n\nThis mean been able to see the display of the Zaurus on the remote and use it to controle the Zaurus with your mouse and keyboard.\n\nExcept being cool and fun, allowing to make snapshot, this can be usefull to type a lot of data in graphical application.\n\nFor console application prefer the use a ssh session! ssh root@zaurus_ip_address\n\n\n\'\'\'On Zaurus Side :\'\'\'\n\nInstall fbvncserver\n\nWhen you want to launch vnc server, on console, launch fbvncserver\n\nfbvncserver -fancy\n\nor\n\nfbvncserver -double\n\n\n\'\'\'On remote side :\'\'\'\n\nLaunch VNC client\n\nvncviewer -encoding \"raw\" zaurus_IP_address:0\n\nWhy \"-encoding raw\"? Duno. Perhaps because fbvnc (Frame Buffer VNC) server is runing on Zaurus and not (\"simple\") vnc server.\n\n\n----\nEnjoy!\n\nzFlorent','utf-8');
