-C3200]]\n| [[Akita]]<br>[[Spitz]]<br>[[Borzoi]]<br>[[Terrier]]\n|}\n|}\n\n|\n{| cellpadding=5\n| bgcolor=\"#ACEDB1\" | <center><font size=\"+1\">\'\'\'HowTos\'\'\'</font></center>\n|-\n| bgcolor=\"#ACEDB1\" |\n{| cellpadding=4 width=100%\n| \n{{HowTos}}\n|}\n|}\n\n|}\n\n</td></tr></table>\n\n\n= Wiki =\n\n10 July 06: The [[ReleaseNotes/Oz3541|3.5.4.1 release]] is out!  [[Clamshell]] owners rejoice.\n\nAlso, we installed [http://www.homelandstupidity.us/software/bad-behavior/installing-and-using-bad-behavior/on-mediawiki/ Bad Behavior] to try to cope with the dramatic increase in spam over the last month.\n\nSome hints on how to use this Wiki more effectively can be found on [[Help:Contents]].\n\n[[Style Guide]] -- some guidelines for adding content to this Wiki.\n\n[[Special:Whatlinkshere/Template:Question|Pages with Questions]]\n\n[[Special:Whatlinkshere/Template:ToDo|Pages with TODOs]]\n\n[[Users|User Pages]]\n\n{{Todo|Format this Wiki section like the rest of the main page.}}','utf-8');
INSERT INTO mw_text VALUES (2366,'= Controlling Spam, Monitoring Changes, etc. =\n\nSee [[Help:Contents]].\n\n= Changing the Sidebar =\n\nTo change the always-visible navigation links, modify [[MediaWiki:Sidebar]].  See [[Help:Sidebar]] for more.  Only admins can edit the sidebar.  See [http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:User_rights wikimedia] for more information.\n\n= Permissions =\n\n[[Special:Makesysop]]\n\n[[Special:Userrights]]\n\nhttp://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:User_rights\n\n= TODO =\n\n* Setup automatic backups for the database and the site repo.  (what about uploaded images?)\n* Test image upload.  This is fairly low priority but might be useful.  Screenshot galleries would be especially nice.\n* Show how to set up mirrors that use svk.  This way, if the database gets corrupted, you can just roll back time until you find a good version.\n* We should probably use categories to help organize things on this site: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Category\n* User [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Interlanguage_links inter-language links] to handle translation.  Current HowTos/DE/USB_Netz is just silly.  Translation efforts appear largely stalled out, however, probably because we don\'t have any well-organized articles to translate.\n\nmuch later:\n\n* Ask someone to create a custom theme.  [http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/MediaWiki_look_and_feel] [http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Skins]  Look to [http://hula-project.org] or [http://www.mono-project.com/Main_Page] for inspiration.  Ensure that the new theme is easily read on Zaruses (even 240 pix wide?)\n\n= Done =\n[[Template:Admin/Done]]:\n{{Template:Admin/Done}}\n\n= Tools =\n\n[[ShowTimestamp]]\n\n= Statistics =\n\n[http://openzaurus.berlios.de/usage/ Site Statistics]\n\n[https://www.google.com/analytics/home/report?rid=554045 Google Analytics]\n\n[http://openzaurus.berlios.de/info.php PHPInfo]','utf-8');
